    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Heresy Supreme</strong> revolves around a combat system that is punishing yet rewarding</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every choice must be weighed; react in time or face a violent end. And when weapons are not enough, turn to dozens of items to curse, confuse, and drive your enemies into despair.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216800/extras/ac6772ea9551d7f836630e7d4a1b1977.poster.avif?t=1771843581\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216800/extras/ac6772ea9551d7f836630e7d4a1b1977.webm?t=1771843581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216800/extras/ac6772ea9551d7f836630e7d4a1b1977.mp4?t=1771843581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Dying Lands</strong> are a place where salvation is always temporary and constantly at risk</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather a party of wretched antiheroes and try to stall the Apocalypse before they betray you and strip you of what little you have. You can’t win. You can only survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216800/extras/5e929a7675dd3f7d32c799ae9270a3c9.poster.avif?t=1771843581\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216800/extras/5e929a7675dd3f7d32c799ae9270a3c9.webm?t=1771843581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216800/extras/5e929a7675dd3f7d32c799ae9270a3c9.mp4?t=1771843581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A perpetually shifting adventure</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built from a large pool of handcrafted situations and quests, constantly rearranged by a semi-procedural system. Enemies, drops, and stats are randomized. Expect no patterns. Expect no mercy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216800/extras/11d343c4cbd16788a0800ebe80fa62c8.poster.avif?t=1771843581\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216800/extras/11d343c4cbd16788a0800ebe80fa62c8.webm?t=1771843581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216800/extras/11d343c4cbd16788a0800ebe80fa62c8.mp4?t=1771843581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mesmerizing art-punk <strong>graphic style</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wretched <strong>world</strong> doomed by an unavoidable apocalypse</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A brutal, haunting <strong>doom metal soundtrack</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple classes,</strong> each radically different in strategy, strengths, and approach</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ARPG elements</strong>. Light on mechanics, heavy on everything else</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
